data.description: Welcome to 430 Saratoga Place. This stunning high-end residence is meticulously crafted to capture the essence of refined living.As you approach this magnificent property, you are greeted by a grand circular driveway, providing a grand entrance befitting the stature of this home. Step inside and be amazed by the attention to detail and high-quality finishes throughout.The newly upgraded fixtures and hardwood floors create an ambiance of elegance. The formal dining room boasts wainscoting and detailed pillars, perfect for memorable gatherings and luxurious entertaining.The two-story living room is adorned with a tile fireplace and built-in shelves, adding both warmth and a touch of architectural beauty. Sunlight pours in through the expansive windows, enhancing the inviting atmosphere of this space.Escape to the primary bedroom, a place of relaxation and comfort. Vaulted ceilings and a reading nook create a serene retreat within your own home. The primary bathroom is a true oasis, featuring double vanities, and tile throughout. Indulge in the walk-in shower or organize your wardrobe with ease in the walk-in closet, complete with custom built-in shelving.Prepare culinary delights in the gourmet kitchen, boasting granite countertops, ample cabinet space, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The elegant tile backsplash and convenient barstool seating add an element of sophistication to this culinary haven.This home offers multiple laundry rooms, as well as a spacious office area and a bonus room. Movie nights will be a true experience in the dedicated theater room.Step into luxury with this magnificent indoor heated pool with LED lighting, diving board, and automatic remote controlled cover in an air-conditioned environment for year round enjoyment for entertaining family fun.All of this and located only 1/4 mile away from a private Cleveland Country Club golf course. Don't miss the opportunity to own this gorgeous residence.
